title: Why I am unranked on TFT?
body: literally just got unranked, even if I finished placement games and got a rank long ago, maybe the first week the game got released.

replies.body: The new season just started.  Everyone's unranked like always happens at the beginning of a new season.  This is normal, not a bug.
As far as i know TFT ranks got hard reset to iron. that might be it
